post_install() {
    cat <<'EOF'
===================================================================
Tiny-DFR has been installed successfully!
Configuration files: /usr/share/tiny-dfr

Compatibility:
  - Xorg: works natively
  - Wayland: Niri, Sway, Hyprland, GNOME (with WindowMonitorPro extension)
    required for the Window Focus Helper to work correctly

Start the service: sudo systemctl start tiny-dfr
===================================================================
EOF
}

